word_group.brief_definition: 绝大多数；绝大多数人；压倒性多数
莫大的挑战；巨大的挑战；艰巨的挑战
压倒性的喜欢；极度的喜爱

bilingual.source: The beauty of the landscape was overwhelming.
bilingual.target: 风景的美丽是压倒性的。

bilingual.source: The support for the new policy was overwhelming.
bilingual.target: 对新政策的支持是压倒性的。

bilingual.source: The evidence against the suspect was overwhelming.
bilingual.target: 对嫌疑人的证据是压倒性的。

bilingual.source: The allure of fame and fortune can be overwhelming.
bilingual.target: 名利的吸引力可能是压倒性的。

bilingual.source: The fans' adoration for the singer was overwhelming.
bilingual.target: 粉丝们对这位歌手的崇拜是压倒性的。

bilingual.source: Financial burdens can be overwhelming for many families.
bilingual.target: 经济负担对许多家庭来说可能是压倒性的。

bilingual.source: She felt an overwhelming sense of relief after the exam.
bilingual.target: 考试结束后，她感到一种压倒性的轻松。

bilingual.source: She was smothered by the overwhelming love of her family.
bilingual.target: 她被家人压倒性的爱弄得窒息的。

bilingual.source: The seduction of power can be overwhelming for some people.
bilingual.target: 权力的诱惑对某些人来说可能是压倒性的。

bilingual.source: The busyness of the city can be overwhelming for newcomers.
bilingual.target: 城市的忙碌对新来的人来说可能是压倒性的。

list.abstract: 《Overwhelming》是2009年8月17日发行的英语歌曲，歌手是Divercia，收录于专辑《Cycle of Zero》。

yingyinNormal.en: God, this adoption stuff is so overwhelming.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天呐，领养这件事真让人无所适从。

yingyinNormal.en: There's so much I don't know. It's overwhelming.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有太多东西我不了解，快把我……搞晕了。

yingyinNormal.en: It's overwhelming. It's for royalty. We are royalty, Rose.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好贵重。这是为皇室做的，我们就是皇室。

yingyinNormal.en: Overconfidence from his robot's massive size and its overwhelming power.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他对机器人大体积超能量的过度自信。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm going to recondition your brain so that the need for completion isn't so overwhelming.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要重建你的大脑思路，让这种对结局的需求得以抑制。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh God, okay. You know what? Opening the presents right now is a little overwhelming right now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们知道吗？拆礼物太刺激了。

yingyinNormal.en: It's like you're a cave person. Rachel, you must get a nanny. You don't know how overwhelming this is going to be.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好像山顶洞人，你得请个奶妈，你不知道带孩子有多累。

yingyinNormal.en: So in the face of overwhelming odds, I'm left with only one option, I'm going to have to science the shit out of this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以在这种悲催情况下，我只剩下一个选择，我得搞搞科研，把这破事儿解决了。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 应该说，这些信息铺天盖地。

examination_example.sentence: Professor Goel already had eight teaching assistants, but that wasn't enough to deal with the <highlight>overwhelming</highlight> number of daily questions from students.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Goel教授已经有了八名助教，但这还不足以应付学生每天提出的海量问题。

examination_example.sentence: The desire for a future reward is <highlight>overwhelming</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对未来奖励的渴望压倒了一切。

examination_example.sentence: This includes professional support from various health and wellness providers if stress is becoming increasingly <highlight>overwhelming</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果压力变得越来越大，这包括来自各种健康和保健提供者的专业支持。

examination_example.sentence: This means they have <highlight>overwhelming</highlight> negative emotions towards the subject, ranging from rage to despair.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这意味着他们对这个话题有着压倒性的负面情绪，从愤怒到绝望。

examination_example.sentence: And studying in a foreign country seems a bit <highlight>overwhelming</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 去异国他乡上学似乎有些让我不知所措。
